#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:333
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RSA_WEAPON_RESTORE\"]/choice[9]/text"
msgstr "Change your mind and check out the regular marketplace instead."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:342
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as you enter the beacon, you're hailed by an RSA Mantis ship nearby:"
" \"I welcome you to our bomb flak store! Here, we selling many bomb flaks! "
"...And other things, because no one is buying them necause theg are thinking"
" they are filthy minelaunchers! They are not!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:345
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_MANTIS_DUMB\"]/text"
msgstr "(Mantis Crew) \"Having anything better?\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:347
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_MANTIS_DUMB\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"You thinking bomb flaks are minelaunchers, huh?! Either that, or you are "
"thinking I having some special, ancient bomb flak made by some, I don't "
"know, sentient cube? But, of course it's the former, right? Well, you are "
"STUPID! And stupid people, even Mantis, must dying!\" The ship powers up its"
" weapons and attacks!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:350
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_MANTIS_DUMB\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Prepare for battle."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:356
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"mantis_rsa\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(RSA Mantis Crew) Your RSA Mantis expresses sympathy for their plight."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:358
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"mantis_rsa\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Thank you! We RSA Mantis know better than anyone else the inner workings "
"of bomb flak! If only others knew same... Maybe we needing to work on "
"marketing? Nah, we just need less stupid people in multiverse! Here, have "
"some scrap.\" The Mantis sends over some supplies, and invites you into "
"their store."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:361
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"mantis_rsa\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Check out their store."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:364
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"mantis_rsa\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before you shop, you still have some time to do something else aboard the "
"ship."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:366
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"mantis_rsa\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:370
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"mantis_rsa\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:378
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_MANTIS_SMART\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"(Smart Mantis Crew) Your Mantis expresses understanding of the difference "
"between minelaunchers and bomb flaks."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:380
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_MANTIS_SMART\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"A fellow Mantis, not of RSA, understanding difference between bomb flaks "
"and minelaunchers? I can't believing it!\" The Mantis' voice lowers to a "
"whisper: \"This weapon not ready for public yet, just prototype. But, I "
"think you deserving of it.\" They send over a bomb flak that seems to be "
"based on a Flak IV! \"Now, there are many more bomb flaks here I'm sure you "
"will love. Come on in!\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:383
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_MANTIS_SMART\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Check out their store."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:386
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_MANTIS_SMART\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before you shop, you still have some time to do something else aboard the "
"ship."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:388
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_MANTIS_SMART\"]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:392
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[@req=\"BLUELIST_MANTIS_SMART\"]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:400
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Check out their store."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:403
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Before you shop, you still have some time to do something else aboard the "
"ship."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:405
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:409
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/choice[4]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:417
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DESTROYED_STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You probably shouldn't have let your Mantis insult them like that, but "
"hindsight is 20/20. All of the bomb flaks inside the ship were destroyed, "
"but at least you can scrap the remains of the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_special_standard.xml.append:422
msgid ""
"data/events_special_standard.xml.append$//event[@name=\"DEAD_CREW_STOREEVENT_RSA_BOMB_FLAKS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You probably shouldn't have let your Mantis insult them like that, but "
"hindsight is 20/20. Inside the cargo-hold, you find the bomb flaks. You also"
" notice a locked door that seems to hold something important, but you can't "
"open it. You content yourself with taking one of the bomb flaks and "
"scrapping the rest of the ship."
